metadata.name: Meta$heroes Genesis #1
metadata.description: WELCOME TO META$HEROES GENSIS, a collection of 3333 unique $uper Heroes born into the Ethereum blockchain. We have been building something special, and now is your chance to be a part of our growing community. Entering our Meta$hero community means joining a family full of investors and NFT enthusiasts who believe in the future of the WEB3. With multiple utilities, marketplace, multiple streams of income opportunities, community DAO and P2E game development. We will have it ALL.
